title: customer service - turning the wrong corner
description:
disaster tracks.
chaos and serenity.
the middle of a bender.
turning the wrong corner.
the pulse of anxiety amplified.
everything on the verge of collapse.
teutonic rhythm drowning in cough syrup.
a body to body, floor filling doorstop rhythmic bloc.
anthems for the young and beautiful.
waiting for the ship that never comes.

RIYL: kompakt, bpitch, villalobos, basic channel, left of center techno
